data.description: Nestled in the picturesque town of Jonesboro, Arkansas, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Located within the sought-after Valley View School District, this lovely home is not only close to local schools but also offers easy access to parks, making it an ideal choice for families. As you approach the house, you'll immediately notice the two-car attached garage, providing ample parking space and added convenience. The well-maintained exterior boasts a combination of rock and siding, giving the home a timeless and welcoming appeal. Upon entering, you're greeted by 1,356 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space, where every detail has been carefully considered. The central heat and air conditioning ensure a comfortable climate year-round, while a wood-burning fireplace in the living room creates a cozy atmosphere on chilly evenings. One of the standout features of this house is the bonus sunroom, a tranquil retreat that allows you to enjoy the views of the expansive backyard.
